FREDERICK SALVUCCI:
Well for politicians

00:21:34.330 --> 00:21:36.510
who get their
votes from workers,

00:21:36.510 --> 00:21:40.570
there's more of a desire
to be a good employer.

00:21:40.570 --> 00:21:45.850
But it's actually inconvenient
to have a subset of workers

00:21:45.850 --> 00:21:51.490
who are largely financed through
subsidy, making higher wages,

00:21:51.490 --> 00:21:54.880
and with better health
care and pension benefits

00:21:54.880 --> 00:21:58.480
than other workers who
